text: For all the complaints the haters have of Blackpink, this is still the greatest girl group in the world and their phenomenal success has paved the way for 4th Gen groups by creating a HUGE market for female Kpop groups. They made it possible for them to achieve global success. The song "Cupid" became virally successful not in Korea but in the western market created by the mind-blowing success of Blackpink.  BP made it possible for them to go to Coachella (Aespa) become ambassadors for luxury European brands BP: Dior, Chanel, YSL, Celine. Bulgari....Hanni: Gucci, Heyin: Louis Vuitton etc. Go to the largest stadiums in numerous countries with all sold out performances having to add more dates and move to larger venues because of the demand. Their "Born Pink Tour" is certified as the most successful tour by ANY girl group. Their music is so different,  their visuals stunning, their stage presence fierce, their off stage personalities hilarious. The first Kpop group I ever encountered was Blackpink. I love them and will always be a blink and am grateful that through them I discovered G-Idle, Red Velvet, IU, Aespa, I've, Le Sserafim, and kimchi.😅🎉❤
